description: {"blocks":[{"key":"75uo9","text":"Generation of 3-dimensional spheroids containing human umbilical vein endothelial cells and human amnion-derived mesenchymal stem cells. The protocol uses an optimized cell ratio to obtain stable spheroids that can be transferred to human platelet lysate-based gels. Within the gels the spheroids form sprouts and interconnect with each other. After grwoth, the spheroids can be fixed in the gel and stained for confocal microscopy.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
guidelines: {"blocks":[{"key":"8d9fa","text":"Critical steps:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"culfo","text":"1) Use primary cells at an early passage","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"74uo5","text":"2) do not handle the hanging drop culture too roughly, also carefully open/close the incubator door","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"90uke","text":"3) take your time while transferring the spheroids to the gel","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bmnop","text":"Carefully pipette the gel mix on the window of the µ-dish (avoid bubbles)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"c0op9","text":"Repeat step 16 until 5 spheroids are transferred to the gel","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4n6k0","text":"Put the µ-dish in a bigger pertridish with PBS (to prevent dehydration of the gels) and incubate at 37 °C, 5% CO2 overnight","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"sub","offset":112,"length":2}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"6jop2","text":"After 24 hours sprouts are visible","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
